lyrics:
Доброта это здорово!
Я люблю печь печеньки
И раздавать из людям!
Я очень счастлив!

[verse]
In a realm where chaos reigns, we rise
Where breakdowns collide and passion ignites
The fusion of metal and hardcore hearts beat
Unleashing our wrath, Metalcore never retreats

[chorus]
Metalcore's our anthem, it's our battle cry
Screaming defiance as we amplify
Raging guitars, pounding drums, and endless screams
Metalcore's fire burns within our veins, it redeems
